      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone who needs affordable wheels, a project, or a dependable runabout with some character. It\u2019s not perfect and it shows its age, but it\u2019s been a handy, useful car and still has plenty to offer the right buyer. If you\u2019re after something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this could be a great fit. Priced fairly to sell and open to a sensible conversation.",
