      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone who wants an affordable driver or straightforward project. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers dependable basic transportation with a proven powertrain layout and a chassis that feels usable and serviceable. Engine starts, runs, and moves out as it should, and the drivetrain delivers the kind of simple, mechanical honesty that makes these worth keeping on the road. Expect visible wear, blemishes, and the sort of issues you\u2019d address over time, but for the money it\u2019s a practical entry point with good parts value and plenty of upside for the next owner. Priced to sell and ideal for someone who knows how to turn a wrench.",
      "price": 5900.0,
